          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1683028165726-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the spaghetti is almost done, reduce the heat to medium and top with <strong>half </strong>of the <strong>grated cheese</strong> (save the rest for later!) and cook, covered, for a final 2 min or until the cheese has melted – this is your <strong>one-pot tomato spaghetti & lean meatballs</strong></p><p>Wash your <strong>salad</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1683028172998-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1683028172998-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
